description: The fund’s investment strategy is to seek to grow capital by tactically investing in other ETFs that invest in equity, bond, and gold based on “relative sentiment” factors. The fund’s portfolio will be tactically allocated among passively-managed U.S. and foreign, developed market, equity ETFs, bond ETFs, and, in some instances, gold exchange-traded products (ETPs). The fund is non-diversified.
name: Relative Sentiment Tactical Allocation ETF
